  "texts": [
    "For the development in this field, readers can refer to a recent review [52].In addition to gradient-based algorithms, Heuristic and deep learning algorithms have also been used to optimize band gaps [41], [53], [54].",
    "Shen et al. [41] designed 2D photonic crystals with largest absolute band gap using genetic algorithm.",
    "During the optimization, fill patterns of pixels in unit cells were encoded in 'chromosomes' with binary digits, corresponding to two dielectric materials.",
    "Then in every generation, populations were generated by selectively mating and mutating current 'chromosomes' to find the global optimum after iterations.",
    "In order to reduce the computational time and make the structures practical for fabrication, a two-stage strategy was introduced."
  ],
